{% extends "::baseUpsell.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}FLO FIT - Lifetime Digital{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="video display-none">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="span-medium-24">
                <div class="video-box">
                    <div id="video"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="lifetime-digital-wrap">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="span-medium-24">
                <h1 class="headline-01">Congratulations!<br> And Here’s What to Do NOW for BIG&nbsp;SAVINGS!</h1>

                <p class="bold font-19">Congratulations on making the decision to get fit with FLO&nbsp;FIT!</p>

                <p>You’re about to experience getting in shape on a whole other level.</p>

                <p>Before we get started, though, I want to give you the opportunity so save some money.</p>

                <p><strong>A&nbsp;LOT of money.</strong></p>

                {% if previousProduct is defined and previousProduct is not null %}
                    {% if previousProduct.trialDays > 7 %}
                        <p>You’ve opted for the monthly billing after your 14-day trial of only ${{ previousProduct.secondPrice }}.</p>
                    {% else %}
                        <p>You’ve opted for the monthly billing after your 7-day trial of only ${{ previousProduct.secondPrice }}.</p>
                    {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                    <p>You’ve opted for the monthly billing after your 7-day trial of only $8.95.</p>
                {% endif %}


                <p>But what if I could show you a way to get <strong>FLO&nbsp;FIT for FREE every month – FOREVER!?</strong></p>

                {% if price is defined and price is not null %}
                    <p>Just click the box below and we’ll bill your credit card – one time and one time only – just ${{ price }}.</p>
                {% else %}
                    <p>Just click the box below and we’ll bill your credit card – one time and one time only – just $37.</p>
                {% endif %}

                <p>And you have 60 days – a full TWO&nbsp;MONTHS – to make absolutely sure you love FLO&nbsp;FIT. Because unless you do, just say the word and I’ll rush every penny right back to you!</p>

                <p>You pay for less than a year of FLO&nbsp;FIT, but you get FLO&nbsp;FIT absolutely FREE for the rest of your life.</p>

                <p><strong>All the videos. All the special reports. All the fat-burning, muscle-toning secrets, training, advice and help</strong> that will put you on the path – and speed you right along -- to the getting and keeping trim, super-sexy body you’ve always wanted.</p>

                <p>How can we afford to do this?</p>

                <p>Our accountant tells me it’s a whole lot easier on her to get just one single payment one time – instead getting a payment every month.</p>

                <p><strong>So save her a little hassle. And save yourself a lot of money.</strong></p>

                <p>Click the box below for money-saving single payment option RIGHT&nbsp;NOW and take advantage of this special one-time offer.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="buy-box">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="span-medium-24">
                    <div class="prices">
                        {#<h4 class="first-price">{{ priceOld }}</h4>#}
                        {#<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>#}
                        <h3 class="second-price">{{ priceNew }}</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="button-card">
                        <a class="button button-danger buy-link-accept" href="{{ linkAccept }}"><i class="tiecons tiecons-basket-shop-buy"></i>Add to order</a>
                        <i class="icon-p icon-paymentmethods"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-center"><strong>Yes! I want to save by getting lifetime access today!</strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="span-large-20 offset-large-2 margin-vertical-30">
                    <a href="{{ linkDecline }}" class="no-link">No thanks. I understand that this is my only opportunity to save big by getting Lifetime Access today and I’m okay with missing out. I understand that after declining this offer, the special Lifetime Access package will never be available in this form again to me at any price... even if I wish to pay more. So realize I’m passing on this forever.</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% endblock %}